Status line for dwm with

- Time
- Battery charge and consumption (might not work evrywhere)
- CPU load
- CPU frequency 
- network load when network is in use

Looks like (idle): 
 | 0.80 | 0% 0% | 77% 8.41W | Thu Aug 22 11:25:02

or (with load):
wlan0: 236.32 kB/s rx, 7.16 kB/s tx  | 1.60 | 52% 54% | 77% 8.52W | Thu Aug 22 11:25:15